# Database Rules

- All schema changes go through migrations, never manual ALTER statements
- Use transactions for multi-table writes
- Add indexes for columns used in WHERE clauses and JOINs
- Implement soft deletes (deletedAt column) for user-facing data
- Table names: plural snake_case (user_profiles, not UserProfile)
- Column names: snake_case (created_at, not createdAt)